---
title: Chicken Sausage Cavatappi Bolognese with Zucchini & Parmesan
description: A bowl of pasta never fails to satisfy—it’s quick, carby, comforting, and our total weeknight go-to. When you add sweet Italian chicken sausage, tender bites of zucchini, and Parmesan to the equation, you’ve reached another level of deliciousness entirely. Ready to enjoy bite after bite of twisty cavatappi pasta cloaked in this creamy, flavor-boosted Bolognese? We thought so.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61f98622422b687c017a9408-0d509f38.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-sausage-cavatappi-bolognese-61f98622422b687c017a9408-41ea258c.pdf
